
= OPERATIONAL ANALYSIS =

=== DEFINITION ===

Before and beyond System/Software requirements, Operational Analysis focuses on the customer needs and goals. Its objective is to ensure good adequacy of System/Software definition with regards to its real operational use.


Outputs of Operational Analysis consist mainly in an &lsquo;operational architecture&rsquo; describing and structuring this need in terms of Actors/Users, their Operational Capabilities and Activities, operational use Scenarios giving dimensioning parameters, operational constraints including safety, security, system life cycle&hellip;.


